onf mechanism from the discussion in <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"164808267\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/3269\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/3269/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/3269\">#3269</a> and <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"172570785\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/3966\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/3966/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/3966\">#3966</a>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Autodetect <code>nvcc</code> version and:\n<ul>\n<li>Set <code>CUDA_TOOLKIT_PATH</code> based on detected version</li>\n<li>Set <code>--expt-relaxed-constexpr</code> iff detected version is &gt;= 7.5.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Set <code>cxx_builtin_include_directory</code> for CUDA headers based on detected include directories, similar to <a href=\"https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel/blob/master/tools/cpp/cc_configure.bzl#L125\"><code>_get_cxx_inc_directories</code></a></li>\n<li>Move remaining checks in <code>configure</code> script into <code>cuda_configure</code> so that the <code>configure</code> script only contains the user interface.</li>\n</ul>", "body_text": "Some improvements to the new CUDA autoconf mechanism from the discussion in #3269 and #3966:\n\nAutodetect nvcc version and:\n\nSet CUDA_TOOLKIT_PATH based on detected version\nSet --expt-relaxed-constexpr iff detected version is >= 7.5.\n\n\nSet cxx_builtin_include_directory for CUDA headers based on detected include directories, similar to _get_cxx_inc_directories\nMove remaining checks in configure script into cuda_configure so that the configure script only contains the user interface.", "body": "Some improvements to the new CUDA autoconf mechanism from the discussion in #3269 and #3966:\n- Autodetect `nvcc` version and:\n  - Set `CUDA_TOOLKIT_PATH` based on detected version\n  - Set `--expt-relaxed-constexpr` iff detected version is >= 7.5.\n- Set `cxx_builtin_include_directory` for CUDA headers based on detected include directories, similar to [`_get_cxx_inc_directories`](https://github.com/bazelbuild/bazel/blob/master/tools/cpp/cc_configure.bzl#L125)\n- Move remaining checks in `configure` script into `cuda_configure` so that the `configure` script only contains the user interface.\n"}